# baseline recipe, estimated from Kelly Mencin (NYC Radio Bakery). 

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oPUux4h4Mf8

300g white flour
75g whole wheat flour
autolyse 30 mins

Levain - starter make 100g of starter
77-78 fahrenheit water

2% fine sea salt
2% instant yeast

after autolyst, add yeast, salt and starter
mix, and rest 30 mins
fold, repeat 3 more times (4 folds 30 mins apart)
Let rest room temp for 3 more hours
Oil pan and initial shape
Gentle gold in pan iwith oil

Let rest 2 hours final proof
Fridge overnight

Proof at 28 celsius for 90 mins
Add toppings
Dimple with drizzle of olive oil
Deck oven 15-18 mins 550 fahrenheit 
